      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available for the serious driver is this mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a documented VANOS service history. This example translates power through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a tight limited-slip differential. The chassis has been optimized for turn-in response with upgraded bushings, and the critical rear subframe reinforcement has been proactively addressed to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. While the exterior displays a light patina reflective of spirited road use, the drivetrain remains in peak operational harmony. It features a factory-correct suspension geometry that provides the telepathic steering feedback and 50/50 weight distribution synonymous with the M division\u2019s golden era.",
